@CleanIlkley @fromspringon @YorkshireWater @EnvAgency CSO =Combined Sewer Overflows
Sewers where foul and surface water drainage are mixed. In heavy rain they overflow and the mixed untreated sewage/surface water is discharged via the CSO directly into water courses and rivers.

